# Components

## Organization

- `src/components/pages/` — page-level compositions (e.g. `HomeIndex.tsx`)
- `src/components/ui/` — shadcn primitives (Button, Card, Tabs, …)
- Feature components at `src/components/` root

## Client vs server

- Add `"use client"` only when using hooks, events, or browser APIs.
- Prefer Server Components for pages; pass translated strings or use `NextIntlClientProvider` (set in layout).

## Styling

- Tailwind CSS 4 + `cn()` from `@/lib/utils`.
- Use CSS variables from `globals.css` for theme tokens.

## RTL

- Arabic sets `dir="rtl"` on `<html>`.
- Keep code, numbers, logos LTR with `OmitRTL` from `@/components/OmmitRlt`:

```tsx
<OmitRTL omitRTL>
  <pre><code>{command}</code></pre>
</OmitRTL>
```

## Theme

- No `next-themes`. Theme: cookie SSR (`src/lib/theme.ts`) + `ThemeProvider` + `ModeToggle`.
- Do not inject blocking scripts for theme flash prevention.

## UI additions

- New shadcn components: follow `components.json` aliases (`@/components`, `@/lib/utils`).
- Icons: `lucide-react`.
